---
// Asymmetric, editorial story section
---

<section class="story section" id="story">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="story-grid">
      <aside class="story-media reveal">
        <figure class="story-figure">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1568254183919-78a4f43a2877?w=1100&q=75"
            alt="Baker shaping dough at dawn"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <figcaption>Shaping dough, 5:00 am</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="story-figure story-figure--offset">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509440159596-0249088772ff?w=900&q=75"
            alt="Sourdough cooling on the counter"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <figcaption>Sourdough, cooling</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </aside>

      <div class="story-content reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Our Story</span>

        <h2 class="story-title">
          A bakery built on
          <span class="italic-serif amber">patience,</span>
          time, and a very good oven.
        </h2>

        <p>
          In 1975, the Millar family opened a small bakery on Donaghadee's High
          Street. No branding consultants, no quarterly reports, no shortcuts —
          just an eight-deck oven, a family recipe for wheaten bread, and the
          stubborn belief that good food takes its time.
        </p>

        <blockquote class="story-quote">
          "If it's worth eating, it's worth doing properly. You can taste the
          rush."
          <cite>— Jim Millar, founder</cite>
        </blockquote>

        <p>
          Fifty years later, the oven is newer and the coffee machine takes up
          more room than it used to. Almost everything else is the same. We
          mill, mix, proof, and bake in the same building. The queue on a
          Saturday morning is the same. The recipe on the sausage roll — the
          one that brought home the Irish Food Award — is the same.
        </p>

        <div class="story-stats">
          <div>
            <span class="stat-num serif">5am</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Daily bake starts</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="stat-num serif">36hr</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Sourdough ferment</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="stat-num serif">4</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Generations baking</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .story {
    background: var(--cream-soft);
  }

  .story-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 5fr 6fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 6rem);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .story-media {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .story-figure {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .story-figure img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 420px;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 1.2s var(--ease-out);
  }

  .story-figure:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }

  .story-figure figcaption {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 14px;
    left: 16px;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    background: rgba(30, 25, 18, 0.72);
    color: var(--cream);
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }

  .story-figure--offset {
    width: 72%;
    justify-self: end;
    margin-top: -40px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .story-figure--offset img { height: 280px; }

  .story-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.4rem);
    margin: 24px 0 28px;
    max-width: 18ch;
  }

  .amber { color: var(--amber); }

  .story-content p {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--warm-grey);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .story-quote {
    display: block;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--amber);
    padding: 12px 0 12px 24px;
    margin: 32px 0;
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.22rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--rich-brown);
  }

  .story-quote cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-style: normal;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--warm-grey);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .story-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding-top: 32px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(61, 35, 20, 0.12);
  }

  .story-stats > div { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }

  .stat-num {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--rich-brown);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--warm-grey);
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .story-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .story-figure--offset { width: 86%; margin-top: -24px; }
    .story-figure img { height: 320px; }
  }
</style>
